e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:27:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fffb2f577b5912ea22770448a5054073957ddd4","tid":1346994,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:28:02.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"cb3f5a61530ac7246a3680ce0043d2779375c2a4","tid":1346994,"uid":193271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"推 真係太少消息 唔知係傳媒夾定想遲少少放定真係被封鎖消息<br />\n現階段只係得文字 無咩圖同片好難推到比人了解"},{"pid":"2f5c5b6694447044f85e6e24161e176dcc0b8731","tid":1346994,"uid":31572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:17:33.000Z","msg":"緊急呼籲，請傳閱以下<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span><span style=\"color: red;\">戰略</span>：<br />\n<br />\n一、 視尋晚嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">白衫</span>軍為<span style=\"color: red;\">恐佈分子</span>，其所作所為乃<span style=\"color: red;\">恐襲</span><br />\n二、<span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察聯合恐怖分子</span>破壞社會，其目的為<span style=\"color: red;\">轉移政府失誤嘅焦點</span><br />\n三、出師必有名，請將光復元朗行動易名<span style=\"color: red;\">全民反恐</span>"},{"pid":"fde1613e5db4524cb43be2ca5cf329e46b606b36","tid":1346994,"uid":276926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"3851aa1567e9d1a349578645d4f1c73ce0c7c231","tid":1346994,"uid":199709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:11:03.000Z","msg":"上環Video 整合 (粗略) <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1</a> <br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=8382f4ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b6ac1c67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=645c22f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=28c21041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=60742685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=036c247d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=43ebd18f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=25982294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=7c2cfd05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=6251ca85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b84f0ca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=f8a0d985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=8615ae5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=12dcf875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=a3b42c93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n黑警用催淚彈直射向記者 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=9500fe3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplePhotographers%2Fphotos%2Fa.1131233677080155%2F1131269430409913%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=c2917105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n（07.21）譴責警察暴力：記者被催